---
import KormanPitchLayout from '@layouts/KormanPitchLayout.astro';
---

<KormanPitchLayout
  title="Korman Autoworks — Brand Identity"
  description="Brand identity guide for Korman Autoworks."
>

  <!-- ======= 1. Hero ======= -->
  <section class="slide slide--km-hero" id="slide-1">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <div class="km-hero-meta fade-in">Brand Identity · v2.0 · March 2026</div>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 480 160" width="460" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="reveal" role="img" aria-label="Korman Autoworks wordmark">
        <text x="240" y="60" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central" font-family="'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif" font-weight="900" font-size="72" letter-spacing="0.08em" fill="#FFFCF0">KORMAN</text>
        <rect x="40" y="96" width="400" height="3" fill="#0066B1"/>
        <rect x="40" y="99" width="400" height="3" fill="#2B115A"/>
        <rect x="40" y="102" width="400" height="3" fill="#C62828"/>
        <text x="240" y="135" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'IBM Plex Mono',monospace" font-size="10" letter-spacing="0.15em" fill="#6F6E69">AUTOWORKS · GREENSBORO, NC · EST. 1978</text>
      </svg>
      <div class="km-hero-tag fade-in">Motorsport Performance · Since 1978</div>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-hint fade-in">
      <div class="scroll-hint__arrow"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 2. 00 Positioning ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-2">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="km-section-num reveal">00</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading reveal">Positioning</h2>
      <div class="km-position-statement reveal">
        Not a BMW shop.<br>A motorsport shop that builds BMWs.<br><span class="km-red">The Ultimate Driving Machine. Finished.</span>
      </div>
      <p class="km-backstory fade-in">Korman Autoworks was founded in 1978 in Greensboro, North Carolina. Before the shop became synonymous with BMW performance, Ray Korman built and raced Lotus and Datsun. The motorsport DNA came first. BMW became the focus because the platform deserved better than the factory was willing to deliver&mdash;and Korman had the racing pedigree to deliver it. Two wins at the 24 Hours of Watkins Glen. IMSA Endurance Championship. Stage I through III packages that turned 2002s and E30s into legends. The identity isn't BMW-exclusive&mdash;it's motorsport-native.</p>
      <div class="km-two-col fade-in">
        <div>
          <div class="km-label">Brand voice</div>
          <p>Confident without arrogance. Technical without jargon. The voice of someone who has won endurance races and doesn't need to tell you unless you ask. Every claim is backed by a dyno sheet or a race result.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="km-label">Brand tension</div>
          <p>Heritage form, modern execution. Oil-stained hands building precision instruments. A Southern speed shop with Group A pedigree. The warmth of a family business with the standards of a factory race team. Patina as proof of life.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 3. 01 Mark — Wordmarks ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-3">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="km-section-num reveal">01</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading reveal">The Mark</h2>
      <p class="km-section-intro fade-in">Three forms, one identity. The wordmark is the primary mark. The roundel is the companion icon. The M-stripe underline bridges them. Each works independently; together they're the full lockup.</p>
      <div class="km-label">The wordmark</div>
      <p class="km-mark-desc">The name IS the mark. Barlow Condensed Black, tracked out, M-stripe underline. Handles 80% of applications: signage, livery, apparel, web, print.</p>
      <div class="km-mark-grid km-mark-grid--3 stagger-children">
        <div class="km-mark-cell km-mark-cell--dk">
          <span class="km-mark-cell__label">Dark</span>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 360 120" width="300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <text x="180" y="52" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central" font-family="'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif" font-weight="900" font-size="58" letter-spacing="0.12em" fill="#FFFCF0">KORMAN</text>
            <rect x="32" y="80" width="296" height="3" fill="#0066B1"/><rect x="32" y="83" width="296" height="3" fill="#2B115A"/><rect x="32" y="86" width="296" height="3" fill="#C62828"/>
            <text x="180" y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'IBM Plex Mono',monospace" font-size="9" letter-spacing="0.15em" fill="#6F6E69">AUTOWORKS · GREENSBORO, NC · EST. 1978</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="km-mark-cell km-mark-cell--lt">
          <span class="km-mark-cell__label" style="color: var(--fx-base-700)">Light</span>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 360 120" width="300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <text x="180" y="52" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central" font-family="'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif" font-weight="900" font-size="58" letter-spacing="0.12em" fill="#100F0F">KORMAN</text>
            <rect x="32" y="80" width="296" height="3" fill="#0066B1"/><rect x="32" y="83" width="296" height="3" fill="#2B115A"/><rect x="32" y="86" width="296" height="3" fill="#C62828"/>
            <text x="180" y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'IBM Plex Mono',monospace" font-size="9" letter-spacing="0.15em" fill="#6F6E69">AUTOWORKS · GREENSBORO, NC · EST. 1978</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 4. 01 Mark — Roundel ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-4">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="km-section-num reveal">01</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading reveal">The Roundel</h2>
      <p class="km-mark-desc fade-in">Four floating quarter-circle chambers separated by negative space&mdash;the metal wall between enamel cells. One blue (TL), one red (BR), two open. The asymmetry is the identity: BMW's roundel is symmetric, Korman's breaks that with a single red chamber. Orientation is fixed, never rotated.</p>
      <div class="km-mark-grid km-mark-grid--4 stagger-children">
        <div class="km-mark-cell km-mark-cell--dk">
          <span class="km-mark-cell__label">Primary · Dark</span>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" fill="none" stroke="#FFFCF0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <g transform="translate(-2,-2)"><path d="M102,102 L102,24 A78,78 0 0,0 24,102 Z" fill="#0066B1"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(2,-2)"><path d="M98,102 L176,102 A78,78 0 0,0 98,24 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(-2,2)"><path d="M102,98 L24,98 A78,78 0 0,0 102,176 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(2,2)"><path d="M98,98 L98,176 A78,78 0 0,0 176,98 Z" fill="#C62828"/></g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="km-mark-cell km-mark-cell--lt">
          <span class="km-mark-cell__label" style="color: var(--fx-base-700)">Primary · Light</span>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" fill="none" stroke="#100F0F" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <g transform="translate(-2,-2)"><path d="M102,102 L102,24 A78,78 0 0,0 24,102 Z" fill="#003D78"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(2,-2)"><path d="M98,102 L176,102 A78,78 0 0,0 98,24 Z" fill="#F2F0E5"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(-2,2)"><path d="M102,98 L24,98 A78,78 0 0,0 102,176 Z" fill="#F2F0E5"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(2,2)"><path d="M98,98 L98,176 A78,78 0 0,0 176,98 Z" fill="#C62828"/></g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="km-mark-cell km-mark-cell--dk">
          <span class="km-mark-cell__label">Monochrome</span>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" fill="none" stroke="#FFFCF0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <g transform="translate(-2,-2)"><path d="M102,102 L102,24 A78,78 0 0,0 24,102 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(2,-2)"><path d="M98,102 L176,102 A78,78 0 0,0 98,24 Z" fill="rgba(255,252,240,0.1)"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(-2,2)"><path d="M102,98 L24,98 A78,78 0 0,0 102,176 Z" fill="rgba(255,252,240,0.1)"/></g>
            <g transform="translate(2,2)"><path d="M98,98 L98,176 A78,78 0 0,0 176,98 Z" fill="rgba(255,252,240,0.35)"/></g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="km-mark-cell km-mark-cell--dk">
          <span class="km-mark-cell__label">Scale</span>
          <div class="km-scale-row">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" fill="none" stroke="#FFFCF0" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(-2,-2)"><path d="M102,102 L102,24 A78,78 0 0,0 24,102 Z" fill="#0066B1"/></g><g transform="translate(2,-2)"><path d="M98,102 L176,102 A78,78 0 0,0 98,24 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g><g transform="translate(-2,2)"><path d="M102,98 L24,98 A78,78 0 0,0 102,176 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g><g transform="translate(2,2)"><path d="M98,98 L98,176 A78,78 0 0,0 176,98 Z" fill="#C62828"/></g></svg>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" fill="none" stroke="#FFFCF0" stroke-width="3"/><g transform="translate(-3,-3)"><path d="M103,103 L103,24 A79,79 0 0,0 24,103 Z" fill="#0066B1"/></g><g transform="translate(3,-3)"><path d="M97,103 L176,103 A79,79 0 0,0 97,24 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g><g transform="translate(-3,3)"><path d="M103,97 L24,97 A79,79 0 0,0 103,176 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g><g transform="translate(3,3)"><path d="M97,97 L97,176 A79,79 0 0,0 176,97 Z" fill="#C62828"/></g></svg>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g transform="translate(-5,-5)"><path d="M105,105 L105,20 A85,85 0 0,0 20,105 Z" fill="#0066B1"/></g><g transform="translate(5,-5)"><path d="M95,105 L180,105 A85,85 0 0,0 95,20 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g><g transform="translate(-5,5)"><path d="M105,95 L20,95 A85,85 0 0,0 105,180 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g><g transform="translate(5,5)"><path d="M95,95 L95,180 A85,85 0 0,0 180,95 Z" fill="#C62828"/></g></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="km-scale-caption">80 · 48 · 24px &mdash; ring drops at smallest</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 5. 01 Mark — Lockup + Livery ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-5">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="km-section-num reveal">01</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading reveal">Lockup &amp; Livery</h2>

      <div class="km-label">Lockup system</div>
      <div class="stagger-children">
        <div class="km-lockup">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="52" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" fill="none" stroke="#FFFCF0" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(-2,-2)"><path d="M102,102 L102,24 A78,78 0 0,0 24,102 Z" fill="#0066B1"/></g><g transform="translate(2,-2)"><path d="M98,102 L176,102 A78,78 0 0,0 98,24 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g><g transform="translate(-2,2)"><path d="M102,98 L24,98 A78,78 0 0,0 102,176 Z" fill="#FFFCF0"/></g><g transform="translate(2,2)"><path d="M98,98 L98,176 A78,78 0 0,0 176,98 Z" fill="#C62828"/></g></svg>
          <div>
            <div class="km-lockup__text">KORMAN</div>
            <div class="km-stripe km-stripe--inline"><span class="km-s-b"></span><span class="km-s-v"></span><span class="km-s-r"></span></div>
            <div class="km-lockup__meta">Autoworks · Greensboro, NC · Est. 1978</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="km-lockup km-lockup--lt">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="52" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" fill="none" stroke="#100F0F" stroke-width="2"/><g transform="translate(-2,-2)"><path d="M102,102 L102,24 A78,78 0 0,0 24,102 Z" fill="#003D78"/></g><g transform="translate(2,-2)"><path d="M98,102 L176,102 A78,78 0 0,0 98,24 Z" fill="#F2F0E5"/></g><g transform="translate(-2,2)"><path d="M102,98 L24,98 A78,78 0 0,0 102,176 Z" fill="#F2F0E5"/></g><g transform="translate(2,2)"><path d="M98,98 L98,176 A78,78 0 0,0 176,98 Z" fill="#C62828"/></g></svg>
          <div>
            <div class="km-lockup__text">KORMAN</div>
            <div class="km-stripe km-stripe--inline"><span class="km-s-b"></span><span class="km-s-v"></span><span class="km-s-r"></span></div>
            <div class="km-lockup__meta">Autoworks · Greensboro, NC · Est. 1978</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="km-label" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg)">Livery application</div>
      <div class="km-livery fade-in">
        <div class="km-livery__panel">
          <div class="km-livery__stripe km-livery__stripe--b"></div>
          <div class="km-livery__stripe km-livery__stripe--v"></div>
          <div class="km-livery__stripe km-livery__stripe--r"></div>
          <div class="km-livery__number">28</div>
          <div class="km-livery__badge">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="36" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="90" fill="none" stroke="#100F0F" stroke-width="4"/><g transform="translate(-3,-3)"><path d="M103,103 L103,26 A77,77 0 0,0 26,103 Z" fill="#003D78"/></g><g transform="translate(3,-3)"><path d="M97,103 L174,103 A77,77 0 0,0 97,26 Z" fill="#F2F0E5"/></g><g transform="translate(-3,3)"><path d="M103,97 L26,97 A77,77 0 0,0 103,174 Z" fill="#F2F0E5"/></g><g transform="translate(3,3)"><path d="M97,97 L97,174 A77,77 0 0,0 174,97 Z" fill="#C62828"/></g></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="km-livery__name">KORMAN</div>
        </div>
        <div class="km-livery__caption">#28 &mdash; historic Korman racing number. All numbers in brand imagery end in -8.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 6. 02 Color ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-6">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="km-section-num reveal">02</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading reveal">Color</h2>
      <p class="km-section-intro fade-in">Three layers. Flexoki warm base is the workshop foundation. Motorsport accents are the identity colors&mdash;earned on track. The warm scale adds material texture. Photographs and the cars provide all other color.</p>

      <div class="km-label">Flexoki base &mdash; workshop foundation</div>
      <div class="km-swatch-row">
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#100F0F"><span class="km-swatch__name">Black</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#100F0F</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#1C1B1A"><span class="km-swatch__name">900</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#1C1B1A</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#282726"><span class="km-swatch__name">850</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#282726</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#343331"><span class="km-swatch__name">800</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#343331</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#403E3C"><span class="km-swatch__name">700</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#403E3C</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#575653"><span class="km-swatch__name">600</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#575653</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#6F6E69"><span class="km-swatch__name">500</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#6F6E69</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--dk" style="background:#B7B5AC"><span class="km-swatch__name">300</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#B7B5AC</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--dk" style="background:#E6E4D9"><span class="km-swatch__name">100</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#E6E4D9</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--dk" style="background:#FFFCF0"><span class="km-swatch__name">Paper</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#FFFCF0</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="km-label">Motorsport accent &mdash; heritage, not allegiance</div>
      <div class="km-swatch-row">
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#003D78"><span class="km-swatch__name">Deep Blue</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#003D78</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#0066B1"><span class="km-swatch__name">Racing</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#0066B1</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--dk" style="background:#4A9DD4"><span class="km-swatch__name">Livery</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#4A9DD4</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt km-swatch--gap" style="background:#2B115A"><span class="km-swatch__name">Violet '73</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#2B115A</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt km-swatch--gap" style="background:#C62828"><span class="km-swatch__name">Motorsport</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#C62828</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--dk" style="background:#E85545"><span class="km-swatch__name">Livery Red</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#E85545</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="km-label">Warm scale &mdash; material texture</div>
      <div class="km-swatch-row">
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#4A2E1B"><span class="km-swatch__name">Walnut</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#4A2E1B</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#7A4E2D"><span class="km-swatch__name">Saddle</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#7A4E2D</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--lt" style="background:#B8652A"><span class="km-swatch__name">Oxide</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#B8652A</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--dk" style="background:#CF7B36"><span class="km-swatch__name">Rust</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#CF7B36</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--dk" style="background:#E09548"><span class="km-swatch__name">Ember</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#E09548</span></div>
        <div class="km-swatch km-swatch--dk" style="background:#D4A373"><span class="km-swatch__name">Clay</span><span class="km-swatch__hex">#D4A373</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="km-card-grid km-card-grid--3 stagger-children">
        <div class="km-rule"><div class="km-rule__title">Dark default</div><div class="km-rule__text">Dark mode is the default. The shop floor is lit by fluorescent tubes, not skylights. Light mode exists for print where dark backgrounds aren't practical.</div></div>
        <div class="km-rule"><div class="km-rule__title">Blue is earned</div><div class="km-rule__text">Racing blue is the primary interactive accent&mdash;links, CTAs, active states. Appears sparingly. Overuse dilutes the motorsport association.</div></div>
        <div class="km-rule"><div class="km-rule__title">Red is rare</div><div class="km-rule__text">Motorsport red appears in the roundel, the M-stripe, error states, and deliberate emphasis. It should feel like a redline indicator&mdash;urgent, purposeful, not decorative.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 7. 03 Typography ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-7">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="km-section-num reveal">03</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading reveal">Typography</h2>
      <p class="km-section-intro fade-in">Three families. Barlow Condensed is the display face&mdash;the text on a homologation plate, a timing board, a manifold decal. IBM Plex Sans is the workhorse body face. IBM Plex Mono handles part numbers, specs, and technical data.</p>

      <div class="stagger-children">
        <div class="km-specimen">
          <div class="km-specimen__label">Display &mdash; Barlow Condensed</div>
          <div style="font-family:var(--km-font-display);color:var(--fx-paper);font-size:clamp(2rem,1.5rem+2vw,3.5rem);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1;margin-bottom:12px;">KORMAN AUTOWORKS</div>
          <div style="font-family:var(--km-font-display);color:var(--fx-paper);font-size:clamp(1.25rem,1rem+1.5vw,2.25rem);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1;margin-bottom:10px;">BMW PERFORMANCE &amp; RACING</div>
          <div style="font-family:var(--km-font-display);color:var(--fx-base-300);font-size:clamp(0.875rem,0.75rem+0.5vw,1.375rem);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1;">SINCE 1978 · GREENSBORO, NC</div>
        </div>

        <div class="km-specimen">
          <div class="km-specimen__label">Body &mdash; IBM Plex Sans</div>
          <div style="font-family:var(--font-body);color:var(--fx-base-200);line-height:1.65;max-width:540px;">Racing at Korman Autoworks is not our primary activity, nor a mere hobby. Our racing activities profoundly improve our BMW provision. The technician working on your car may be the same one that prepared our entries that twice won the 24 Hours of Watkins Glen. Whether you drive on the track or the highway, we prepare your car for long-term satisfaction.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="km-specimen">
          <div class="km-specimen__label">Technical &mdash; IBM Plex Mono</div>
          <div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--fx-base-300);font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;">ENGINE: M20B25 · DISPLACEMENT: 2494cc<br>BORE × STROKE: 84mm × 75mm<br>KORMAN STAGE II: +18HP / +12 lb-ft<br>PART NO: KAW-M20-STG2-R01<br>DYNO SHEET: 2026-03-15 · RUN 04 · PULL 3/3</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======= 8. 04 M-Stripe ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-8">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="km-section-num reveal">04</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading reveal">The M-Stripe</h2>
      <p class="km-section-intro fade-in">The tri-stripe is the connective tissue across all touchpoints. Blue, violet, red&mdash;the original 1973 palette, before BMW replaced the violet with dark blue. It references motorsport heritage while being distinctly Korman. It appears as a thin accent, never as decoration.</p>

      <div class="km-stripe-showcase stagger-children">
        <div>
