      <p class="km-section-intro fade-in">Every car on this list exists because BMW wouldn't build it&mdash;or hadn't built it yet. The pattern: take the best engine of its generation, put it in the chassis where it belongs.</p>

      <div class="km-label">Ray Korman &mdash; Personal Builds</div>
      <div class="stagger-children">
