          <div class="km-build__why">BMW announced the M3 Sport Evolution in December 1989&mdash;S14 bored to 95mm and stroked to 87mm for 2,467cc at 238hp. Paul Rosche's answer to the DTM arms race. Ray Korman had already built a stroked S14 in Greensboro. He independently arrived at the same conclusion as BMW's engine development chief&mdash;and got there first.</div>
